            <div id="equity" class="tab-content active">
                <div class="grid">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px;">üü¢ Positive Inflows Strategy</h3>
                        <p style="color: #d0d0e8; margin-bottom: 15px;">When capital inflows are strong (like US in Sep-Dec 2024)</p>
                        <div class="flow-indicator">
                            <span class="flow-label">Bias</span>
                            <span class="flow-value flow-positive">Bullish</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-indicator">
                            <span class="flow-label">Setup</span>
                            <span class="flow-value">Long large-caps (SPY, QQQ)</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flow-indicator">
                            <span class="flow-label">Duration</span>
                            <span class="flow-value">2-4 weeks</span>
